    <item>
      <title>罗斯的达达认为市场面临“重大下行风险”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-11/roth-s-darda-sees-significant-downside-risk-to-markets-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[罗斯首席经济学家兼宏观策略师迈克尔·达达表示，无论经济衰退与否，市场都存在下行风险，并警告称，如果“人工智能炒作”对生产力的推动作用令人失望，风险市场可能会持续波动。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-11/roth-s-darda-sees-significant-downside-risk-to-markets-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 11 Sep 2024 11:50:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
